<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201013/2e0798f1e1924eaaa086ae75aee95553.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《扎朶那河谷》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201013/3292363400db487b9c2a7fd9262da32d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《春天的小河流》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201013/30237f4d36c5432a808f7ee2e79dbd18.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
